  "linked_names": [],
  "evidence_excerpts": [
    {
      "text": "51\n30\n\na fundamentally different world. Not only that, a vast \"story\" is disclosed, having to do with a basic dialectical strife. It is, as I realized when I read the E.B. Macro article on \"Messiah + Messianic movements\" quite literally a Messianic, apocalyptic view of reality of a Zoroastrian, Qumran, 4th Gospel, N.T. nature. It is sacred history, not secular, + it consists of constants (eide) not flux spatiotemporal sets of accidents. Valis, then, is the messenger, the revealer: hence the Logo",
      "matched_alias": "Messiah",
      "term_id": "TERM_messiah",
      "term_name": "Messiah",
      "term_slug": "messiah"
    },
